Coding Tips:

1. Start with Brute-force
2. Pattern Detection
3. Time complexity to APPROACH
4. N-Dimensional Observation
5. Pre-Simplification
6. Naming Convention
7. Parallel Visualisation (MUST)


DP:
    Every solution for sub-problem must be correct.
    Solution order helps in debugging


GREEDY:
    One parameter dependent problem
        1. heap
        2. sorting

    Two parameter dependent problem
        1. heap + sorting
        sort with respect to one parameter + optimize with respect to another parameter
